HEADWORD: Terrestrify
<hw>Ter*res"tri*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>terrestris</ets> terrestrial + <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To
convert or reduce into a condition like that of the earth; to make
earthy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

